You owe me 50 million.

2734
01:21:31,875 --> 01:21:32,708
Var är de?

2735
01:21:31,875 --> 01:21:32,708
Where are they?

2736
01:21:32,791 --> 01:21:34,875
De skulle vara här.

2737
01:21:32,791 --> 01:21:34,875
They were supposed to be here and…

2738
01:21:34,958 --> 01:21:37,666
Vi får väl åka upp några våningar.

2739
01:21:34,958 --> 01:21:37,666
I guess we'll have to go up a few floors.

2740
01:21:38,250 --> 01:21:39,916
-There they are.
-What?

2741
01:21:38,416 --> 01:21:39,791
-De är ju där.
-Va?

2742
01:21:40,583 --> 01:21:44,125
Nej, jag tycker inte
att det ser ut som de.

2743
01:21:40,583 --> 01:21:44,125
No, I don't think that looks like them.

2744
01:21:44,208 --> 01:21:46,291
-Det är de. Kom igen!
-Jorma!

2745
01:21:44,208 --> 01:21:46,291
-It's them. Come on!
-Jorma!

2746
01:21:46,375 --> 01:21:48,208
Vadå "lugna ner mig"? Va?

2747
01:21:46,375 --> 01:21:48,208
What do you mean "calm down", huh?

2748
01:21:48,291 --> 01:21:49,875
Du har ju förstört allting!

2749
01:21:48,291 --> 01:21:49,875
You've ruined everything!

2750
01:21:49,958 --> 01:21:52,791
Norinder är borta.
Han var som en far för mig.

2751
01:21:49,958 --> 01:21:52,791
Norinder is gone.
He was like a father to me.

2752
01:21:53,500 --> 01:21:55,958
[på engelska]
Ingen brådska, men skulle vi kunna…

2753
01:21:53,500 --> 01:21:55,958
No rush, but can we just…

2754
01:21:56,666 --> 01:21:58,791
hurry up a little? I can just…

2755
01:21:56,875 --> 01:21:59,916
-Kan vi skynda på lite?
-Håll käften.

2756
01:21:58,875 --> 01:21:59,916
Shut up.

2757
01:22:00,000 --> 01:22:01,125
[på svenska] Ja.

2758
01:22:00,000 --> 01:22:01,125
Yep.

2759
01:22:02,958 --> 01:22:04,333
Svara, då.

2760
01:22:02,958 --> 01:22:04,333
Pick up!

2761
01:22:04,416 --> 01:22:07,333
Jag är ju ingen pilot.
Jag blev tvungen att dra.

2762
01:22:04,416 --> 01:22:07,333
As you might have realized,
I'm not a pilot. I had to split.

2763
01:22:07,416 --> 01:22:09,416
Men jag lovar att fixa fram pengarna.

2764
01:22:07,416 --> 01:22:09,416
But I promise, I'll get the money.

2765
01:22:09,500 --> 01:22:10,625
Du ljuger!

2766
01:22:09,500 --> 01:22:10,625
You're lying!

2767
01:22:10,708 --> 01:22:12,750
-[hisspling]
-[Jorma] Polis!

2768
01:22:11,458 --> 01:22:12,750
Police!

2769
01:22:12,833 --> 01:22:14,916
Drop the gun!

2770
01:22:13,250 --> 01:22:15,083
Släpp vapnet! Släpp vapnet!

2771
01:22:15,000 --> 01:22:16,041
Hit the floor!

2772
01:22:15,166 --> 01:22:17,333
[rop, skott som avfyras, automateld]

2773
01:22:18,958 --> 01:22:20,083
Return fire!

2774
01:22:19,541 --> 01:22:21,416
[polis] Besvara eld! Besvara eld!

2775
01:22:21,500 --> 01:22:24,541
Påskjut! Påskjut!

2776
01:22:21,500 --> 01:22:22,833
Take cover!

2777
01:22:23,416 --> 01:22:24,541
Take cover!

2778
01:22:25,291 --> 01:22:27,375
-Return fire!
-Damn, he's getting away!

2779
01:22:25,416 --> 01:22:27,375
Besvara eld! Fan, han kommer undan!

2780
01:22:28,250 --> 01:22:29,083
Great!

2781
01:22:28,666 --> 01:22:33,666
[på engelska] Härligt!
Så, trevligt att göra affärer med dig.

2782
01:22:30,083 --> 01:22:33,666
So, nice doing business with you.

2783
01:22:35,708 --> 01:22:36,750
Herregud.

2784
01:22:35,708 --> 01:22:36,750
Oh, my God.

2785
01:22:36,833 --> 01:22:39,958
-Okej, det här är inte bra.
-Jag vet.

2786
01:22:36,833 --> 01:22:39,958
-Okay, this is not good.
-I know.

2787
01:22:40,041 --> 01:22:41,250
Tv:n är borta.

2788
01:22:40,041 --> 01:22:41,250
The TV is gone.

2789
01:22:41,750 --> 01:22:43,166
The tail went the wrong way.

2790
01:22:42,000 --> 01:22:43,583
Svansen gick åt fel håll.

2791
01:22:43,666 --> 01:22:45,250
De kommer fan att komma undan.

2792
01:22:43,666 --> 01:22:45,250
They're getting away!

2793
01:22:48,166 --> 01:22:50,958
-Vet du vad? Hasse ska inte komma undan.
-Conny.

2794
01:22:48,166 --> 01:22:50,958
-Hasse is not getting away.
-Conny!

2795
01:22:55,583 --> 01:22:56,583
But…

2796
01:22:57,208 --> 01:22:58,041
Conny.

2797
01:22:57,208 --> 01:22:58,166
Conny!

2798
01:22:59,375 --> 01:23:01,666
Eh… Jag ska bara kolla…

2799
01:23:00,166 --> 01:23:01,708
I'm just going to check…

2800
01:23:12,041 --> 01:23:13,666
[på engelska] Hej igen. Förlåt.

2801
01:23:12,041 --> 01:23:13,666
Excuse me. Hello again. Sorry.

2802
01:23:14,875 --> 01:23:15,916
Flytta på er.

2803
01:23:14,875 --> 01:23:15,916
Could you move?

2804
01:23:16,000 --> 01:23:17,125
Hej! Eller…

2805
01:23:16,000 --> 01:23:17,125
Hi! Or…

2806
01:23:17,958 --> 01:23:18,958
Conny!

2807
01:23:17,958 --> 01:23:19,083
Conny!

2808
01:23:19,166 --> 01:23:21,708
-What the fuck?
-Please, can you move? Thank you!

2809
01:23:20,041 --> 01:23:22,375
[på engelska] Kan ni flytta på er? Tack!

2810
01:23:24,125 --> 01:23:25,458
Jesus Christ!

2811
01:23:24,125 --> 01:23:25,458
Jesus Christ!

2812
01:23:26,041 --> 01:23:27,291
-Police!
-Police!

2813
01:23:26,250 --> 01:23:27,291
-Polis!
-Polis!

2814
01:23:27,375 --> 01:23:29,541
Visa händerna! Visa händerna!

2815
01:23:27,375 --> 01:23:29,708
-Show us your hands!
-Lie down!

2816
01:23:30,708 --> 01:23:33,041
