2817
01:23:30,708 --> 01:23:33,041
Against the wall! Show us your hands!

2818
01:23:33,958 --> 01:23:35,875
Josef! Perfekt!

2819
01:23:33,958 --> 01:23:35,875
Josef… Perfect!

2820
01:23:35,958 --> 01:23:38,666
Ni är svansen.
Det var vi som ringde, för att…

2821
01:23:35,958 --> 01:23:38,666
You're the tail. We called, 'cause…

2822
01:23:38,750 --> 01:23:39,708
Det är Helena!

2823
01:23:38,750 --> 01:23:39,708
It's Helena!

2824
01:23:41,291 --> 01:23:42,291
[engelska] Förstått?

2825
01:23:41,291 --> 01:23:42,291
Do you understand?

2826
01:23:42,375 --> 01:23:46,000
Jag har bevis på en tv
som har blivit skjuten, men…

2827
01:23:42,375 --> 01:23:45,291
I have proof on a TV… that was shot,

2828
01:23:45,375 --> 01:23:48,541
but you have to believe me. Josef?

2829
01:23:46,083 --> 01:23:48,541
Du måste tro mig. Josef?

2830
01:23:49,666 --> 01:23:51,083
Säg åt dem att släppa mig.

2831
01:23:49,666 --> 01:23:51,083
Tell them to let me go.

2832
01:23:51,916 --> 01:23:52,750
Josef!

2833
01:23:51,916 --> 01:23:52,875
Josef!

2834
01:23:57,625 --> 01:23:58,458
Stanna, sa jag!

2835
01:23:57,625 --> 01:23:58,458
I said stop!

2836
01:24:00,541 --> 01:24:02,041
Hasse, stanna!

2837
01:24:00,541 --> 01:24:02,041
Hasse, stop!

2838
01:24:03,625 --> 01:24:04,625
Hasse!

2839
01:24:04,125 --> 01:24:05,375
Hasse!

2840
01:24:07,416 --> 01:24:08,416
Aj!

2841
01:24:07,416 --> 01:24:08,416
Ow!

2842
01:24:10,541 --> 01:24:11,375
Vänta!

2843
01:24:10,541 --> 01:24:11,375
Wait!

2844
01:24:12,291 --> 01:24:13,125
Wait!

2845
01:24:13,208 --> 01:24:14,333
Ursäkta!

2846
01:24:13,208 --> 01:24:14,333
Excuse me!

2847
01:24:23,541 --> 01:24:25,750
Skottkärran? Vad fan…

2848
01:24:23,541 --> 01:24:25,750
The wheelbarrow? Dammit…

2849
01:24:29,000 --> 01:24:30,333
Conny! Conny!

2850
01:24:29,000 --> 01:24:30,333
Conny!

2851
01:24:30,833 --> 01:24:32,500
-Stop.
-Cut it out!

2852
01:24:34,166 --> 01:24:36,458
Vad fan håller du på med?

2853
01:24:34,166 --> 01:24:37,041
What the hell are you doing? You can't…

2854
01:24:36,541 --> 01:24:38,041
Du kan inte… Ah!

2855
01:24:38,125 --> 01:24:39,666
-[Conny stönar]
-[Hasse] Aj!

2856
01:24:44,916 --> 01:24:45,833
Vänta! Vänta!

2857
01:24:44,916 --> 01:24:46,541
Wait!

2858
01:24:45,916 --> 01:24:47,916
-Vänta! Vänta!
-[en hane spänns]

2859
01:24:50,833 --> 01:24:51,958
Va?

2860
01:24:53,541 --> 01:24:54,791
Nu räcker det!

2861
01:24:53,541 --> 01:24:54,791
That's enough!

2862
01:24:57,166 --> 01:24:58,375
Spelet är slut!

2863
01:24:57,166 --> 01:24:58,375
The game's up.

2864
01:24:58,458 --> 01:25:00,041
Spelet är slut?

2865
01:24:58,458 --> 01:25:00,041
"The game's up"?

2866
01:25:00,125 --> 01:25:03,458
Ja, det blev lite lökigt,
men du fattar vad jag menar!

2867
01:25:00,125 --> 01:25:03,458
Yes, that was a bit corny,
but you know what I mean.

2868
01:25:04,166 --> 01:25:05,000
Du borde ha…

2869
01:25:04,166 --> 01:25:05,000
You should have…

2870
01:25:05,833 --> 01:25:07,166
[Hasse stönar av smärta]

2871
01:25:08,000 --> 01:25:09,500
…stannat i fängelset!

2872
01:25:08,000 --> 01:25:09,416
stayed in prison!

2873
01:25:12,291 --> 01:25:13,791
Nu kommer jag att försvinna.

2874
01:25:12,375 --> 01:25:13,791
I'm going to disappear.

2875
01:25:16,666 --> 01:25:18,333
Och vi kommer inte att ses mer.

2876
01:25:16,666 --> 01:25:18,333
And we won't meet again.

2877
01:25:21,458 --> 01:25:22,541
Du förlorade, Conny.

2878
01:25:21,458 --> 01:25:22,541
You lost, Conny.

2879
01:25:23,250 --> 01:25:25,625
Och jag är uppenbarligen
den stora vinn… aren.

2880
01:25:23,250 --> 01:25:25,625
And I'm obviously the big winner--

2881
01:25:25,708 --> 01:25:27,250
[polis] Vapen!

2882
01:25:25,708 --> 01:25:27,250
Gun!

2883
01:25:27,333 --> 01:25:29,250
Ner på golvet! Ner på golvet!

2884
01:25:27,333 --> 01:25:29,250
Hit the floor!

2885
01:25:29,333 --> 01:25:33,291
-Händerna på ryggen! Släpp vapnet!
-Ligg ner. Upp med händerna.

2886
01:25:29,333 --> 01:25:31,000
Hands on your back! Drop the gun!

2887
01:25:31,083 --> 01:25:33,291
Lie down! Show me your hands!

2888
01:25:39,000 --> 01:25:39,833
[dörr stängs]

2889
01:25:56,750 --> 01:25:57,791
Conny!

2890
01:25:56,750 --> 01:25:57,791
Conny!

2891
01:26:01,291 --> 01:26:03,125
-God, it's…
-Now we're even.

2892
01:26:01,791 --> 01:26:03,125
Nu är vi kvitt.

2893
01:26:12,666 --> 01:26:13,750
[Diana] Vad sa du?

2894
01:26:13,833 --> 01:26:16,125
-Du är så…
-[Jorma] Jag gör bara mitt jobb.

2895
01:26:13,833 --> 01:26:16,125
-You're such a--
-I'm just doing my job!

2896
01:26:16,208 --> 01:26:18,875
-[Diana] Fattar du inte?
-Det spelar ingen roll. Nej.

2897
01:26:16,208 --> 01:26:18,083
-Don't you get it?
-It doesn't matter.

2898
01:26:18,166 --> 01:26:19,916
-No.
-You seriously think I did it?

2899
01:26:18,958 --> 01:26:21,166
[Diana] Tror du att jag har gjort det?

2900
01:26:21,250 --> 01:26:23,375
Så bra, Jorma. Bra jobbat.

2901
01:26:21,250 --> 01:26:23,375
Well done, Jorma. Good work.

2902
01:26:23,458 --> 01:26:24,375
-Helena?
-Ja?

2903
01:26:23,458 --> 01:26:24,375
-Helena?
-Yes?

2904
01:26:24,458 --> 01:26:27,916
Jag har bevis. Jag vet allt om dig.
Jag vet exakt vad du har gjort.

2905
01:26:24,458 --> 01:26:25,291
I have proof.

2906
01:26:25,375 --> 01:26:27,916
I know it all, everything you've done!

2907
01:26:28,000 --> 01:26:29,666
Alla kommer att få se…

2908
01:26:28,000 --> 01:26:29,666
Everyone will see--

2909
01:26:36,208 --> 01:26:38,166
-[Josef] Är du inte klok? Vad fan…
-Va?

2910
01:26:36,250 --> 01:26:38,166
-Are you out of your mind?
-What?

2911
01:26:38,250 --> 01:26:42,500
-Vad gör du för nånting?
-Ja, nu "tejsade" jag henne lite.

2912
01:26:38,250 --> 01:26:39,833
I mean… What are you doing?

2913
01:26:39,916 --> 01:26:40,833
So now I…

2914
01:26:41,416 --> 01:26:42,500
tasered her a bit.

2915
01:26:42,583 --> 01:26:46,875
-Alltså, det här är ju ett gravt…
-Nej, det är…

2916
01:26:42,583 --> 01:26:45,333
I mean, this is an extremely serious…

2917
01:26:45,416 --> 01:26:47,750
No, it is… I agree.

2918
01:26:46,958 --> 01:26:51,708
Jag håller med dig,
men det är en polismördare.

2919
01:26:47,833 --> 01:26:51,708
But this is a police murderer.

2920
01:26:51,791 --> 01:26:54,958
Jag kan inte hjälpa det.
Jag tar det personligt. Det är…

2921
01:26:51,791 --> 01:26:54,958
I can't help it.
I'm taking it personally. It's…

2922
01:26:55,041 --> 01:26:57,250
-Men hur tänker du?
-Just nu, inte alls.

2923
01:26:55,041 --> 01:26:57,250
-What were you thinking?
-I wasn't.

2924
01:26:57,333 --> 01:26:59,416
Nu väntar jag på att hissen ska komma.

2925
01:26:57,333 --> 01:26:59,416
I'm just waiting for the elevator.

2926
01:27:04,000 --> 01:27:05,458
SERVER ROOM

2927
01:27:16,500 --> 01:27:19,250
-Did you get something keto?
-What? No.

2928
01:27:16,666 --> 01:27:19,250
-Hittade du nån keto, eller?
-Va? Nej.

2929
01:27:19,916 --> 01:27:20,791
Jo! Jo!

2930
01:27:19,916 --> 01:27:20,791
Yes.

2931
01:27:21,333 --> 01:27:24,333
-Jag blev proppmätt.
-Vad håller du på med?

2932
01:27:21,333 --> 01:27:22,625
I'm stuffed.

2933
01:27:23,291 --> 01:27:24,333
What are you doing?

2934
01:27:26,083 --> 01:27:28,791
I just need to… do something.

2935
01:27:26,125 --> 01:27:28,791
Jag skulle bara behöva göra en grej här.

2936
01:27:28,875 --> 01:27:32,083
Det tar två minuter. Är det okej?

2937
01:27:28,875 --> 01:27:32,083
It'll take two minutes. Is that okay?

2938
01:27:32,166 --> 01:27:33,208
Okej.

2939
01:27:32,166 --> 01:27:33,208
Okay.

2940
01:27:33,291 --> 01:27:35,041
Ja. Perfekt.

2941
01:27:33,291 --> 01:27:35,041
Right. Perfect.

2942
01:27:36,000 --> 01:27:37,000
Hallå?

2943
01:27:36,000 --> 01:27:37,000
Hello?

2944
01:27:37,958 --> 01:27:39,625
Du får inte vara här inne!

2945
01:27:37,958 --> 01:27:39,625
You can't be in here!

2946
01:27:39,708 --> 01:27:42,000
Skit i henne. Hon är dum i huvudet.

2947
01:27:39,708 --> 01:27:42,000
Ignore her. She's stupid.

2948
01:27:44,291 --> 01:27:46,666
Är det tungt? Ska jag…

2949
01:27:45,000 --> 01:27:46,666
Is she heavy? Should I…

2950
01:27:47,250 --> 01:27:51,416
Skulle du kunna hjälpa mig
och hålla i tv:n?

2951
01:27:47,250 --> 01:27:51,416
Could you help me hold the TV?

2952
01:27:51,500 --> 01:27:52,666
-Javisst.
-Ja.

2953
01:27:51,500 --> 01:27:52,666
-Sure.
-Yes.

2954
01:27:54,250 --> 01:27:55,208
Vad gör du?

2955
01:27:54,250 --> 01:27:55,208
What are you doing?

2956
01:27:55,291 --> 01:27:57,458
-Då ska vi se. Hiss.
-Du får komma ut nu!

2957
01:27:55,291 --> 01:27:57,458
-Let's see, elevator…
-Get out of there!

2958
01:27:57,541 --> 01:27:58,541
Hiss…

2959
01:27:57,541 --> 01:27:58,541
Elevator…

2960
01:27:59,666 --> 01:28:00,750
Vad ska du göra?

2961
01:27:59,666 --> 01:28:00,750
What are you doing?

2962
01:28:01,333 --> 01:28:02,250
INGEN SIGNAL

2963
01:28:03,958 --> 01:28:06,583
Det är en lång historia, men…

2964
01:28:03,958 --> 01:28:05,708
Well, it's a long story, but…

2965
01:28:06,666 --> 01:28:08,000
Jag jobbar på Elgiganten.

2966
01:28:06,666 --> 01:28:08,000
I work at Elgiganten.

2967
01:28:08,083 --> 01:28:10,458
Stackars människa.
Det här blir ju inte kul.

2968
01:28:08,083 --> 01:28:10,500
Poor thing. This won't be fun.

2969
