Fritagning av fånge,
mord, drogförsäljning… Herregud.

2970
01:28:11,375 --> 01:28:14,750
Freeing a convict, murder, drug sales…
My God.

2971
01:28:14,833 --> 01:28:17,541
-Diana berättade en del grejer.
-Det kan jag tänka mig.

2972
01:28:14,833 --> 01:28:17,541
-Diana told me some things.
-Yes, I can imagine.

2973
01:28:17,625 --> 01:28:18,875
Som handlade om dig.

2974
01:28:17,625 --> 01:28:18,875
They were about you.

2975
01:28:21,666 --> 01:28:23,333
Så där.

2976
01:28:21,666 --> 01:28:23,333
There we go.

2977
01:28:24,250 --> 01:28:26,750
Jag vet inte vad du håller på med, men…

2978
01:28:24,250 --> 01:28:26,166
I have no idea what you're doing, but…

2979
01:28:26,833 --> 01:28:28,416
-Det ser jävligt coolt ut.
-Ja.

2980
01:28:26,833 --> 01:28:27,750
It looks cool.

2981
01:28:28,500 --> 01:28:29,375
SMART-TV HITTAD

2982
01:28:31,625 --> 01:28:33,375
Öppna dörren! Det är polisen!

2983
01:28:31,625 --> 01:28:33,375
Open the door! It's the police!

2984
01:28:35,458 --> 01:28:37,791
Det är lugnt. Jag är med dig.

2985
01:28:35,458 --> 01:28:36,291
Don't worry.

2986
01:28:36,791 --> 01:28:38,000
-I'm with you.
-Yeah.

2987
01:28:39,208 --> 01:28:40,541
Nu öppnar du dörren!

2988
01:28:39,208 --> 01:28:41,125
Open the door!

2989
01:28:41,708 --> 01:28:43,125
Jag älskar it.

2990
01:28:41,708 --> 01:28:43,125
I love IT.

2991
01:28:47,416 --> 01:28:48,500
Här. Ta grejerna.

2992
01:28:47,416 --> 01:28:48,500
Here. Take the stuff.

2993
01:28:50,208 --> 01:28:51,916
[polis] Nej. Vi bryter upp dörren.

2994
01:28:50,208 --> 01:28:51,250
We'll break through!

2995
01:28:53,583 --> 01:28:56,375
-Ska jag?
-Ja, så kan man också göra. Kom igen.

2996
01:28:53,583 --> 01:28:56,458
-Do I…
-Yes, that's one way to do it. Come on.

2997
01:28:58,083 --> 01:29:00,750
Polis, lägg dig ner! Ner på golvet!

2998
01:28:58,083 --> 01:29:00,750
-Police, get down!
-Wait!

2999
01:29:00,833 --> 01:29:01,833
Vänta!

3000
01:29:05,125 --> 01:29:05,958
Shit.

3001
01:29:07,958 --> 01:29:09,041
Titta. Här är jag.

3002
01:29:07,958 --> 01:29:09,041
Look, I'm here.

3003
01:29:09,125 --> 01:29:11,541
Lägg dig ner! Lägg dig ner!

3004
01:29:09,125 --> 01:29:11,541
On the floor!

3005
01:29:11,625 --> 01:29:13,083
Ligg still!

3006
01:29:11,625 --> 01:29:13,083
Lie down!

3007
01:29:13,166 --> 01:29:15,583
Se på mig. Se på mig. Josef!

3008
01:29:13,166 --> 01:29:15,583
Look at me. Josef!

3009
01:29:16,500 --> 01:29:18,041
-Jag älskar dig.
-Håll käften.

3010
01:29:16,500 --> 01:29:18,041
-I love you.
-Shut up.

3011
01:29:18,125 --> 01:29:19,125
Josef.

3012
01:29:18,125 --> 01:29:19,125
Josef!

3013
01:29:21,500 --> 01:29:23,291
[handklovar låses]

3014
01:29:23,375 --> 01:29:25,041
-Nej.
-Vi tar det sen.

3015
01:29:23,375 --> 01:29:26,083
-No.
-No, we'll talk about it later.

3016
01:29:25,125 --> 01:29:27,416
Vi tar det sen. Vi tar allting sen.

3017
01:29:26,166 --> 01:29:28,833
We'll talk about everything later.
That's fine.

3018
01:29:28,000 --> 01:29:28,833
Det blir bra.

3019
01:29:28,916 --> 01:29:29,833
Alla är lugna.

3020
01:29:28,916 --> 01:29:29,833
Stay calm.

3021
01:29:29,916 --> 01:29:31,666
-Jag är med honom.
-Ja, eller hur!

3022
01:29:29,916 --> 01:29:31,666
-I'm with him.
-Yeah, right.

3023
01:29:31,750 --> 01:29:34,875
Det är 9270 här. Kan du upprepa det där?

3024
01:29:31,750 --> 01:29:34,875
This is 9270. Can you repeat that?

3025
01:29:34,958 --> 01:29:37,125
Helena Malm, gripen?

3026
01:29:34,958 --> 01:29:37,125
Helena Malm, arrested?

3027
01:29:37,208 --> 01:29:39,666
Ja, 7080, kom. Det stämmer.

3028
01:29:37,208 --> 01:29:39,666
Yes, 7080, over. That's correct.

3029
01:29:39,750 --> 01:29:42,875
Helena Malm är alltså huvudmisstänkt…

3030
01:29:39,750 --> 01:29:42,875
Helena Malm is our main suspect…

3031
01:29:48,583 --> 01:29:53,000
Akta nu. Jag är skadad! Fattar ni?
Aj! Jag kan gå själv!

3032
01:29:49,416 --> 01:29:53,000
I'm injured. Don't you get it?
Ow! I can walk on my own.

3033
01:29:53,083 --> 01:29:54,041
Josef!

3034
01:29:53,083 --> 01:29:54,041
Josef!

3035
01:29:54,125 --> 01:29:55,833
-Josef!
-Tyst.

3036
01:29:54,125 --> 01:29:55,833
-Josef!
-Be quiet.

3037
01:29:55,916 --> 01:29:56,916
Josef!

3038
01:29:55,916 --> 01:29:56,916
Josef!

3039
01:29:57,791 --> 01:29:59,000
Prata inte med henne!

3040
01:29:57,791 --> 01:29:59,000
Don't talk to her!

3041
01:30:03,083 --> 01:30:05,958
-Hej. Hur mår du?
-Bra.

3042
01:30:03,083 --> 01:30:06,000
-Hi. How are you?
-Good.

3043
01:30:08,625 --> 01:30:10,083
Jag skulle ha lyssnat på dig.

3044
01:30:08,625 --> 01:30:10,083
I should've listened to you.

3045
01:30:10,916 --> 01:30:12,416
Det borde du ha gjort.

3046
01:30:10,916 --> 01:30:12,000
You should have.

3047
01:30:16,166 --> 01:30:18,166
[känslofylld musik]

3048
01:30:26,458 --> 01:30:28,291
-Kom igen.
-Ja. Yes. Ja.

3049
01:30:26,458 --> 01:30:28,125
-Come on.
-Yes.

3050
01:30:31,375 --> 01:30:34,333
[Josef] Det har kommit in
en hel del ny information.

3051
01:30:31,375 --> 01:30:34,333
A lot of new information has surfaced.

3052
01:30:53,541 --> 01:30:56,083
PRISON

3053
01:30:56,833 --> 01:30:58,583
[en häst gnäggar avlägset]

3054
01:30:58,666 --> 01:30:59,500
[barn 1] Kolla!

3055
01:30:58,666 --> 01:30:59,500
Look!

3056
01:31:00,458 --> 01:31:02,833
[barn 2] En häst! Den kommer hitåt!

3057
01:31:00,458 --> 01:31:02,833
A horse! It's coming this way!

3058
01:31:08,708 --> 01:31:10,500
Är inte det där din pappa?

3059
01:31:08,708 --> 01:31:10,500
Isn't that your dad?

3060
01:31:11,333 --> 01:31:12,333
Jo.

3061
01:31:11,333 --> 01:31:12,333
Yes.

3062
01:31:12,416 --> 01:31:14,250
[barn 3] Varför bromsar han inte?

3063
01:31:12,416 --> 01:31:14,250
Why doesn't it stop?

3064
01:31:14,333 --> 01:31:15,875
Akta er!

3065
01:31:14,333 --> 01:31:15,291
Look out!

3066
01:31:15,916 --> 01:31:17,833
Get out of the way!

3067
01:31:15,958 --> 01:31:17,833
-Flytta på er!
-[skrik]

3068
01:31:18,875 --> 01:31:20,500
Julia, det går bra!

3069
01:31:18,875 --> 01:31:19,708
It's okay!

3070
01:31:20,583 --> 01:31:22,958
-Pappa, hoppa av!
-Stanna, säger jag!

3071
01:31:20,583 --> 01:31:22,375
-Dad, get off!
-Stop, I said!

3072
01:31:23,041 --> 01:31:24,041
Ptro!

3073
01:31:25,833 --> 01:31:26,708
Aj!

3074
01:31:25,833 --> 01:31:26,708
Ouch!

3075
01:31:30,083 --> 01:31:31,666
Har du köpt hästen?

3076
01:31:30,083 --> 01:31:31,666
Did you buy the horse?

3077
01:31:31,750 --> 01:31:34,666
Nej. Jag fick bara låna den av en kompis.

3078
01:31:31,750 --> 01:31:34,041
No, I borrowed it from a friend.

3079
01:31:34,750 --> 01:31:35,791
Hon där.

3080
01:31:34,750 --> 01:31:35,791
That lady.

3081
01:31:35,875 --> 01:31:37,250
POLICE

3082
01:31:38,666 --> 01:31:40,041
-Tack.
-Ja.

3083
01:31:38,708 --> 01:31:40,041
-Thank you.
-Yeah.

3084
01:31:43,000 --> 01:31:46,208
-[barn] Skynda dig, då.
-Jag kommer! Jag vill också vara med!

3085
01:31:43,000 --> 01:31:45,791
-Hurry up.
-I'm coming, wait for me!

3086
01:31:46,291 --> 01:31:49,875
Pappa sa bara att han hade lite ont
i ryggslutet. Annars är det okej.

3087
01:31:46,375 --> 01:31:49,875
Dad said that his coccyx is hurting,
but he's okay.

3088
01:31:49,958 --> 01:31:51,291
[barn] Vad är det för nåt?

3089
01:31:49,958 --> 01:31:51,208
What's that?

3090
01:31:52,875 --> 01:31:54,875
That went well.

3091
01:31:52,958 --> 01:31:54,875
Det där gick ju… bra.

3092
01:31:55,458 --> 01:31:56,500
Ja.

3093
01:31:55,458 --> 01:31:56,500
Yeah…

3094
01:31:56,583 --> 01:31:59,625
["Hooked on a Feeling"
med Björn Skifs spelas]

3095
01:32:06,166 --> 01:32:08,541
-Vad i helvete håller du på med?
-Vad gör du?

3096
01:32:06,166 --> 01:32:08,333
-What the hell are you doing?
-Yeah?

3097
01:32:08,416 --> 01:32:09,833
-What?
-Are you insane?

3098
01:32:08,625 --> 01:32:11,583
Är du inte klok?
Rider in bland barn på det där sättet?

3099
01:32:09,916 --> 01:32:11,583
Riding among our kids like that?

3100
01:32:11,666 --> 01:32:14,000
-Jag kan…
-Du ska inte upp på en häst.

3101
01:32:11,666 --> 01:32:14,458
-I can…
-If you can't ride, don't get on a horse.

3102
01:32:14,083 --> 01:32:17,416
-Det har varit lite struligt…
-Du bör få fängelse för det här.

3103
01:32:14,541 --> 01:32:17,416
-I've had some trouble…
-You should go to prison.

3104
01:32:17,500 --> 01:32:19,208
-Jag lovar dig.
-Ja.

3105
01:32:17,500 --> 01:32:19,208
-I guarantee it.
-Yeah.

3106
01:32:19,291 --> 01:32:20,958
Hoppas att du har en bra advokat.

3107
01:32:19,291 --> 01:32:20,958
I hope you have a good lawyer.

3108
01:32:24,166 --> 01:32:25,500
Ja, det var ju…

3109
01:32:24,291 --> 01:32:25,375
Well, that was…

3110
01:32:27,083 --> 01:32:28,166
…synd.

3111
01:32:27,083 --> 01:32:28,166
a shame.

3112
01:35:48,458 --> 01:35:53,458
Subtitle translation by: Lisbeth Pekkari

